---
title: Beef Rump & Peppercorn Gravy with Veggie Mash & Tomato Salad
description: There are some hidden gems in tonight’s dinner. The juicy beef rump has been coated in a rich peppercorn gravy; it makes for an easy way to a decadent dish. And this isn’t any ordinary mash, we’ve added carrot and garlic to bring it to the next level. Your taste buds will be spoilt for choice!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
